{"id":2376,"date":"2025-04-10T04:24:49","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T04:24:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/?p=2376"},"modified":"2025-04-11T03:09:31","modified_gmt":"2025-04-11T03:09:31","slug":"ngay-hoi-cong-dong-ve-bao-ton-chim-di-cu-tai-huyen-kim-son-ninh-binh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/ngay-hoi-cong-dong-ve-bao-ton-chim-di-cu-tai-huyen-kim-son-ninh-binh\/","title":{"rendered":"NG\u00c0Y H\u1ed8I C\u1ed8NG \u0110\u1ed2NG V\u1ec0 B\u1ea2O T\u1ed2N CHIM DI C\u01af T\u1ea0I HUY\u1ec6N KIM S\u01a0N, NINH B\u00ccNH"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y 12-13\/03\/2025, Trung t\u00e2m H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec \u0110\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (WildAct) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c <strong><em>&#8220;Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean truy\u1ec1n b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n chim di c\u01b0&#8221;<\/em><\/strong> t\u1ea1i hai x\u00e3 Kim Trung v\u00e0 Kim \u0110\u00f4ng, t\u1ec9nh Ninh B\u00ecnh. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a chim di c\u01b0 trong h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n chim di c\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2379\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-1024x769.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-768x577.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-1536x1153.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01028-2048x1538.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-2380\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/20250312_143654-2048x1536.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat g\u1ea7n 100 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia, bao g\u1ed3m l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb. Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i mang t\u00ednh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c cao, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 chim di c\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. C\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed vui v\u1ebb m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n chim di c\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n g\u0169i, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn tr\u1ef1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda m\u00e0 chim di c\u01b0 \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<p>Qua \u0111\u00f3, g\u1ea7n 200 \u1ea5n ph\u1ea9m truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao t\u1eb7ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n, g\u1eedi g\u1eafm nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u00fd ngh\u0129a.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2378\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/z6417158547632_950c409018afee1aed2ab606d4688e12-2048x1536.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-2377\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-1024x769.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-768x577.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-1536x1153.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/DSC01120-2048x1538.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><br \/>\nS\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a chim di c\u01b0 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c s\u0103n b\u1eaft v\u00e0 suy gi\u1ea3m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i chim n\u00e0y. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng tham gia v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u0103n b\u1eaft, bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n, ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 chim hoang d\u00e3 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 chim di c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e2ng cao nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 v\u00e0 chim di c\u01b0 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i, mong r\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n chim di c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y 12-13\/03\/2025, Trung t\u00e2m H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00ec \u0110\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (WildAct) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c &#8220;Ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 tuy\u00ean truy\u1ec1n b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n chim di c\u01b0&#8221; t\u1ea1i hai x\u00e3 Kim Trung v\u00e0 Kim \u0110\u00f4ng, t\u1ec9nh Ninh B\u00ecnh. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao nh\u